Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:21.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:35.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:47.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:57.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:10.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:23.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我从头开始翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴,非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心得满心飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴,非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心得满心飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:02:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压抑不住的喜悦 在我的心里飞舞着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领家教费的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是…是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下礼拜再麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,下礼拜见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,她忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我忘了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是上次响子忘了带走的 能不能请你帮我还给她?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好,我是御龟寿司店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少钱?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4300圆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,4300圆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特地拟定的计划泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家教费 妈妈忘了给你家教费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥,家教费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家教费…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#14 太好了五代!和响子首次约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间过得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这里已经一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正比较有改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有五代考上大学这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然内涵还是没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装作若无其事,装作若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一付若无其事的态度…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…她睡着了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是来偷吃她豆腐的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,我怎么睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道 反正我也没有睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他看到我的糗样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚你有空吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起出去吃顿饭,好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天领到打工钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无法请你 吃什么豪华大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过当然是我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0K…是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,六点钟碰头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是“MA.MAISON” 你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,六点MA.MAISON见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,六点豆藏见 (“豆藏”音近“MA.MAISON”)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了,太棒了,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都听见了说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他记得我来这里 今天刚好满一年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟响子约会了 要穿什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都还没说耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不是今晚要喝酒 就是要疯一疯,对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真惊人,你猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我已经有约了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要给管理员开个派对 庆祝她就任一周年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子真无情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以罗,大家要喝个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应怎么这么冷淡?你不方便吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我已经有约了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你是主角耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能稍微来露个脸? 六点钟在豆藏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,豆藏?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他约六点钟的时候 在豆藏碰头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,不说就算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正到了六点就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要举办宴会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你耳朵真好啊 原来你不只是牙齿会发光而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是爱说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要开个派对 庆祝她就任满一周年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?我不是房客耶 这不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是会费制的,所以要交钱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会偏偏选在同一家店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代如果机灵一点 选别的地方就好了说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿哪一件衣服去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(MA.MAISON)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像来得太早了,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量喝,喝个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,主角请坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧,来吧 管理员先干一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我等一下还有约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经超过六点了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,五代怎么没来呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻馆的人 全部都会来,不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子最近忙着交女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去幽会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十分了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,反正女生常常迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耐着性子等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,我又赚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩子 好像是五代的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到七点,如果她还没来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续等到八点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在等的人到底是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就干脆老实招出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经七点了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个烂家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然放你鸽子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过份了,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们约在小酒馆见面啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该是约在MA.MAISON吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是车站附近的咖啡店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么听来还真的蛮像的 MA.MAISON和豆藏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MA.MAISON,豆藏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快点赶去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经七点多了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能抬去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可以去,我不让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也拜托一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经等了一个多小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是被甩了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐,我要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我实在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,五代,你在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么穿成这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你还在这里干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在车站前面柏青哥店 隔壁的咖啡店里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是响子搞错地方了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是五代那里的管理员?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你是五代的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问,你有没有看到五代?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代今天好像去约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得那个女生 好像叫小津江
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟小津江?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 二话不说马上就冲过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他结婚以后 一定会被老婆管得死死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟小津江…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟小津江约会?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是稍微晚点来 他居然马上掉头去找别人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,要不要跟我一起去喝酒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再喝一家,再喝一家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,我陪你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不跟五代讲话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,四个人,有位子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店很便宜 烤饭团好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四位请里面坐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…小津江?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天不是跟五代在一起吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪…阪本,你刚才说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,难道他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位客人好像怪怪的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经打烊了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿去擦一擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一年前 我们第一次见面时你穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你一直等我等到现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要哭了,我没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是让你等了三个小时…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦,我真的不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微靠过来一点好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了,在这种气氛下 我只要很自然地搂着她就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法 我迟到了那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 原来你在豆藏等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道 该怎么向你道歉才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:22:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么棒的气氛 今年大概不可能会再有了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我要尽可能地 尽可能地绕远路…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,两位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你突然冲出去 我们很担心就赶过来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来好像没有必要来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,管理员会淋湿的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我一起撑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.29,0:22:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.53,0:22:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,明天见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,今天真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.08,0:22:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会淋湿的,快进来躲雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:22:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了,我没有在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很自然地…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想趁这个机会吃我豆腐 你实在太低级了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然不会被气氛给陶醉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气得牙痒痒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想变成他那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代在大学校庆的时候 听说要表演人偶剧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大家要一起去看他表演
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:24:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“危险的两人人偶剧! 我已经不行了”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会,我不会演人偶剧…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,救命啊,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:06.78,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:35.69,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}为何你能如此若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:43.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}光只是眨个眼 就能让我悸动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:51.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}使我身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:25:06.30,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}明明已经可以相爱 偏偏时机还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:18.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}我快要忍受不了 快要变成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:23.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}真是痛苦的折磨

